cu.explanation_en: Setting integrity_algorithms[1] to an invalid enum value 'nia7' will cause security negotiation failure and connection establishment issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting force_256qam_off to 2 exceeds the valid range (0 or 1) and will cause 256QAM modulation configuration errors leading to transmission failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 force_256qam_off 設定為 2 超過有效範圍（0 或 1），會導致 256QAM 調製配置錯誤並造成傳輸失敗。
